  "serviceDescription": "With AWS Billing Conductor, you only pay for the pro forma billing records you generate. AWS Billing Conductor gives you the ability to model your billing in a way that more closely matches your organizational structure while retaining the existing billing relationship you have with AWS. To achieve this alternative view of your billing data, the AWS Billing Conductor generates a second, pro forma version of your billing records, consistent with your desired account segmentation, rate management, and custom line items.",
